    <section id="id1166546469806">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id6476436"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Learning Outcome 5:</emphasis></emphasis>The learner will be able to collect, summarise, display and critically analyse data in order to draw conclusions and make predictions, and to interpret and determine chance variation.</para>
      <para id="id8967834"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Assessment Standard 5.5:</emphasis></emphasis> We know this when the learner examines ungrouped numerical data to determine the most frequently occurring score (mode) and the midpoint (median) of the data set in order to describe central tendencies.</para>
    </section>
